```bash
~/.claude/skills/openclaw-skills/bin/openclaw-review-log '{"skill":"plan-eng-review","timestamp":"TIMESTAMP","status":"STATUS","unresolved":N,"critical_gaps":N,"issues_found":N,"mode":"MODE","commit":"COMMIT"}'
```

从完成摘要中替换值：
